parameters:
She is Karin-dono, who has just joined our dojo. As the
assistant master of this dojo, please allow me to introduce
her--

Yes! Nice to meet you, my name is Karin. I will be under
your care from today at the dojo.

Ho ho, the dojo uniform suits you well. This dojo is open
not only to samurai but also to townspeople. There is no
distinction of social status when it comes to learning the
sword. Please dedicate yourself to your swordsmanship.
Thank you very much! I will do my best!

...Oh? Could it be that you are the daughter of Chuutaro-
dono?
Eh!? You know of my father, sensei?

I remember now. It was about 13 years ago. Chuutaro-dono
came to learn the sword at this dojo, bringing you along as
a toddler.
My father came to this dojo...?

Ah, yes. His intense and practical swordsmanship overwhelmed
even me. For a while, Chuutaro-dono became an assistant
master here as a live-in student. He swung the wooden sword
with such speed it was invisible to the eye; he didn't seem
like an ordinary townsman at all. He was truly strong.
Is that so? This is the first time I've heard of it.

In these peaceful times, the world has shifted towards
cultivating the spirit, but if one wields a sword, they must
aim to win against their opponent. That's why this dojo
places emphasis on actual combat.

In the practice area in the back, I, the assistant master,
will be your opponent, so please don't hesitate to come at
me.
Understood. Please go easy on me!

\c[17]--You can now use the "Practical Training Area" at the back
right of the dojo! \c[0]

If you're interested in swordsmanship, we welcome women as
well. If you wish to become stronger, actual combat
experience is paramount above all else. Work hard and
accumulate practice, Karin-dono.

In the practice area beyond here, you can train to take the
enemy from behind, and your EXP will increase. If you wish
to advance your level, it would be good to take on the
challenge.

Put more spirit into it and thrust deeper! You're holding
back!

Oh, what an unusual visitor. If you're interested, you
should watch the practice. This dojo has the most students
in Edo. It should serve as good training for swordsmanship.

Haa... haa... It feels good to sweat a lot after a vigorous
practice.

Come on, come on, if you stay there, you'll be in the way of
practice. It's dangerous to enter the striking distance
during practice.
I'm going to eat a lot and get stronger~

Edo is bustling with swordsmanship. Even the daimyo on their
alternate attendance duty frequent the dojos.

Do you need something? Perhaps, young lady, you wish to
enroll in our dojo? If you want to join, it will cost 3000
mon.

(Swordsmanship, huh... It might be good to train and become
stronger...)
Enroll in the swordsmanship dojo【3000 mon】
剣術道場に入門する【３０００文】

My name is Karin! I'm interested in swordsmanship, so please
let me join this dojo! Please!

Oh, are you serious? It's rare for a girl to wish to enroll.
No, no, you're welcome here.
I've prepared the money. Please, let me join!
--Karin paid 3000 mon as the enrollment fee.
...I've tried on the training outfit, does it suit me?

Um... Instructor, is this correct? I'm not used to wearing
hakama and such.

Ah, my apologies! You look fine and there's no problem! Now
that you've joined, feel free to walk around the dojo.
There's also a 【Combat Training Area】 in the back right.
Feel free to use it.

I'm sorry. I'm not really feeling up to it right now... I'll
ask again another time.
Yes! That torso slash just now was a point, right?

To think you would score a point against me, the assistant
instructor... My, my. Karin-dono, your swordsmanship is
truly splendid. It hasn't been that long since you started,
and yet you've become so strong so quickly.

Ah, thank you very much! All the sparring practice at the
dojo paid off\I[15]

--Karin wiped the sweat dripping from her forehead with a
hand towel.

(...Phew. This is bad. I'm getting too excited... and
starting to feel lewd...)

--? What's the matter, Karin-dono? Your cheeks are so
flushed... Could it be a cold?
師範代を誘惑する\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

\c[27]Main event count +1, vaginal ejaculation +1, lewdness level
+3\c[0]

(No, this is bad! I'm getting indecent thoughts in the dojo!
Calm down, my heart...! Stay composed...!)

Hello, assistant master. You're full of energy today as
well.
...? What's wrong, assistant master? Your face is all red...

No, it's nothing! The other day, I was terribly rude--! To
make such a mistake with you, who are yet to be married...!

Sigh... Yes, that's true... But it's my first time with you,
assistant master, so...
師範代　経験数　結果

Ah... Don't worry about it too much. I'm quite experienced,
so--
Wha-What...! Have you been with that many men?

Yes, it's embarrassing to say, but I've been with about
\V[2] men so far...

～～～～！！With \V[2] men!? (Is... Is this the moral standard of
young women these days... Hmm...)
師範代　経験数　結果
What's wrong, master? Your face is getting even redder...?

--No, it's nothing! Well then... Do you wish to practice
again today, Lady Karin?
稽古をつけてもらう\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

...I'm sorry. I have other things to do today. Please let me
know another time.
Speak to the assistant instructor \c[27][H Event]\c[0]
師範代に話しかける\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]
\c[27]Number of times having sex +1, Creampie +1, Lewdness +3\c[0]

Oh, Lady Karin. You've come to the dojo again today. Well
done.
It seems quite lively at the dojo today, doesn't it?

Yes... There's going to be a match soon to decide the next
master of the dojo.
Eh? A match to decide the dojo master...?

Indeed. The current master is retiring. This dojo values
actual swordsmanship, so the position of master isn't
hereditary. We will have a match, and the strongest disciple
will become the new master.

Wow! So that means you, the Assistant Master, will become
the next master, right?

Hmm... I hope so, but... I tend to be weak under pressure...
When it comes to important matches, I suddenly get stomach
pains and am more faint-hearted than I appear...

Really? That's surprising, considering you have a larger
body than most...

Ugh... It's tough when you put it that way... I need to go
to the restroom...

Haha, just kidding, Master. Could you start our practice
session now?

Ah, then let's begin. I'm counting on you today as well,
Lady Karin--

--The two of them took their bamboo swords, bowed to each
other, and began their practice.

Hmm! A splendid shinai split! That's enough practice for
today--!

Phew... Hah...! Thank you for the practice, Master! I worked
up a good sweat today.

Yes. Well... about today... Do you have any plans after
this? Are you free?

Ahaha\I[15] It's rare for you to ask me out, Assistant
Master?
No... Somehow I can't get you out of my mind since then...

I might as well say I've fallen for you. Would you consider
dating me as your suitor?
～～～～！(What should I do! Is this a confession...!?）

I'm sincerely asking you with my head bowed--! What is your
answer, Lady Karin...?

...I'm flattered by your feelings, but for someone of noble
samurai family like yourself to fall for a town girl like
me... If it's about marriage between a samurai and a
townsfolk...

That's not an issue. If a samurai and a townsfolk were to
marry, becoming adopted as a daughter into another family
would make her equal in status as a samurai's daughter. So
there's no problem regarding social standing.

Yes. Even a former shogun married a townsfolk's daughter in
such a manner... What do you say, Lady Karin? Would you live
here with me at this dojo?
Snuggle up to the assistant instructor \c[10][Assistant Instructor End]\c[0]
師範代に寄り添う\c[10]【師範代エンド】\c[0]

I'm sorry! I have... important things I must do right now,
so I can't marry at this time! I'm truly sorry!
--Karin bowed her head and left the dojo.
--Karin got caught up in the swordsman's practice swings!

Even with a wooden sword, a bad hit can be serious. You
mustn't carelessly enter the range of the sword during
practice, understood?
I'm so sorry, sensei... I was too careless...

[Note: If you defeat a sparring partner more than 30 times
at the practice grounds and then defeat an opponent three
times in a row, you can acquire a new combat technique.]
